After seeing some feedback, is this now ready to put in (some comments on namign elsewhere)? I saw one comment for a different packaging but that seemed to be for a specific use.  I don't think we wil be providing the one-and-only way to package Jena libraries for OSGi; we can provide a "frequently useful" form.

If so, as a new module, I'd like to see a proposal to dev@ that stands out.  This new functionality in delivery is a high ceremony point, and the naming is very user visible (we hope!)

@stain - That make sense?
